title: The Underdog Show - Complete Series + Extras
description:
~~~The Underdog Show~~~

A complete DVD rip of the complete collector's edition, with all the extras.

Also included are VHS rips of the Underdog Show when it was airing on Nickelodeon in 1992. Complete with all the old Nickelodeon commercials and everything, if that's what you're interested in.

DVD ripped episodes are all in XviD format, 1000kbps.
VHSrips are all in h264, 1300kbps.
Extra intros included are in WMV format.

Enjoy, and please seed.
